flowchart TD
    Start([run() 触发 prepareEnvironment]) --> Web{WebApplicationType}

    Web -->|"SERVLET"| ServletEnv[StandardServletEnvironment]
    Web -->|"REACTIVE"| ReactiveEnv[StandardEnvironment]
    Web -->|"NONE"| StdEnv[StandardEnvironment]

    ServletEnv --> PS1[加载 servletConfigInitParams]
    ServletEnv --> PS2[加载 servletContextInitParams]
    ServletEnv --> PS3[加载 JNDI 属性]

    StdEnv --> PS4[加载系统属性 SystemProperties]
    StdEnv --> PS5[加载系统环境变量 SystemEnvironment]

    PS1 --> Merge[合并为 MutablePropertySources]
    PS2 --> Merge
    PS3 --> Merge
    PS4 --> Merge
    PS5 --> Merge

    Merge --> YML[加载 application.yml<br/>application.properties<br/>按 profile 过滤]
    YML --> Active[解析 spring.profiles.active]
    Active --> Env[得到 ConfigurableEnvironment]
    Env --> Event[发布 ApplicationEnvironmentPreparedEvent]

    classDef startNode fill:#e3f2fd,stroke:#1565c0,stroke-width:2px
    classDef psNode fill:#fff3e0,stroke:#ef6c00
    classDef envNode fill:#e8f5e9,stroke:#2e7d32,stroke-width:2px
    class Start startNode
    class PS1,PS2,PS3,PS4,PS5 psNode
    class Env,Event envNode
